# Plan Location

When creating or updating plan files for work across **core2ai**, **api2ai**, and **db2ai**:

- Always store plans under **`core2ai/.cursor/plans/`**.
- Do not keep project plans only in global locations (for example `~/.cursor/plans`) without also copying them into that folder.
- Prefer stable, descriptive filenames so plans are easy to find.
- Obsolete plans are removed manually by the maintainer; do not move plans to `done/` or delete them without being asked.
